; [Dark+ Theme for Pico Logo Editor]
; [Sets palette slots 240-253 to match]
; [the VS Code Dark+ colour scheme.]
; []
; [Usage: load "darkplus.theme]
; []
; [Editor semantic colours in text/editor palette slots]
setpalette 3 [212 212 212]
